{"tid":255883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《成報》辦公室遭追租收樓","createTime":"2017-05-24T06:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T06:22:02.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ee3437068b92a6c6744a7992ff5943cfee962d3","tid":255883,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T06:22:02.000Z","msg":"《成報》位於觀塘開源道的辦公室，其業主入稟高等法院指租用單位[的香港傳媒集團控股有限公司自今年3月起欠租，要求追討2個月租金54.8萬元並要求對方交出物業。<br />\n<br />\n原告為利是發投資有限公司，被告為由《成報》主席谷卓恆擁有的香港傳媒集團控股有限公司。入稟狀透露，原告是觀塘開源道48號威利廣場23樓8個單位及2個車位的業主，去年6月與被告簽3年租約，月租約27.4萬元。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170524/56735493\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170524%2F56735493&d=IZWl12S5z6lUnueYSkvqYZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=9c3508c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170524%2F56735493&h=a4bbb11c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170524/56735493</a>"}]}